userdoc.notice: Minimal interface for interacting with an ERC-20 token.

devdoc.details: This contract does not implement full cross-chain messaging but demonstrates basic deposit (lock) and withdrawal (release) mechanisms.

params._token: The address of the ERC-20 token that will be used in the bridge.

params.amount: The amount of tokens to deposit.

withdraw(address,uint256).details: Only the admin (bridge operator) can trigger withdrawals.

params.amount: The amount of tokens to withdraw.
params.user: The address of the user to withdraw tokens for.
